[SN]TITLE[SN]
British adventurer finishes 'world's toughest race'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
British adventurer Sir Ranulph Fiennes has become the oldest Brit to complete the gruelling desert race, the Marathon des Sables.

